original_title: Diane Horner Country Hip Hop Dancing
overview: Hip Hop is the hottest thing in dancing today. It's showing up in clubs from New York to LA. Now country dance goes Hip Hop. Who would have imagined it? But that's exactly what's happening... Country Hip Hop. Diane Horner, America's best country line dance teacher, will teach you this dance craze right in your own home. You'll learn great Hip Hop steps and moves... before they're taught in your favorite club!
tagline: It's the hottest line dancing in the world!
title: Diane Horner Country Hip Hop Dancing
